snippet.textDisplay:
It would be cool to win, because I have always loved and admired makeup and the way it can make you feel. Few years back I got lucky and I was able to get a side job in a store with bunch of make-up therefore I not only had little extra money to spend on it but I was also around it all the time and I got to experience all the launches and all the exciting stuff.
But now I am studying in med school out of my home country, so all my spare money goes towards rent, food, textbooks and thing related to school. Because I am not in my home country I don't have my side job with makeup anymore, therefore there is not any extra money to be spent on new makeup. Don't get me wrong, I wouldn't change med school for anything, I am beyond blessed to be able to study something I have always dreamed of. But when it comes to my love for makeup, even though I didn't want to, I had to put it aside for a bit. Not because I don't have time. Trust me, I wake up 1 and half hour earlier only so I can enjoy my makeup routine. But it is the money that is the show stopper. Therefore it would be the coolest to win this giveaway so my love for makeup wouldn't have to be pushed aside.

I would be forever grateful. Love you most!

snippet.textDisplay:
Hey Tati,
My husband and I have been stationed over seas in Japan now for three years, and when we first moved I was extremely depressed and was diagnosed with PTSD, during which time I gained almost 40 pounds and became extremely self conscious and more depressed. I eventually found your channel this year and started experimenting with makeup and started to feel prettier again. Makeup was the only thing at the time that made me feel beautiful again which allowed me to start coming out of my depression. In June, I tried your vitamins and made the commitment to start eating better, taking better care of myself again from the inside out and I have been able to finally lose almost 30 pounds. I haven't felt this good in so long, regardless of whether I win the give away or not I wanted to say thank you for what you do. Since I don't have a lot of extra money to spend on make up and skin care stuff it would be cool to be able to win to be able to continue learning how to do my makeup and taking care of my skin.
